{"name":"Fiona Alavara","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"IronVale","alignment":"Lawful Good","hitDice":"15","armorName":"mage armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":8,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"18","chaPoints":"18","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Roll Call","desc":"At the start of [MON]'s turn, the players vote on a **target**. In the event of a tie, Fiona gains an extra action and both players become targets."},{"name":"Emergency Powers","desc":"[MON]'s # of reactions = political capital."}],"actions":[{"name":"Referendum","desc":"All creatures [MON] can see must make a **DC [CHA SAVE]** wisdom save, or make a weapon/spell attack against the target. If a creature is unable to make the attack, Fiona gains **political capital**."},{"name":"Retribution","desc":"The target must make a **DC [CHA SAVE + 1]** wisdom save, or take an action that [MON] chooses. This will expend resources such as spell slots."},{"name":"Entente","desc":"[MON] and the target telepathically agree to not attack each other. [MON] gains **political capital**."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[{"name":"Emergency Meeting","desc":"[MON] expends a **political capital** to change the target of an attack/spell. The players vote on a **different** target. In the event of a tie, [MON] chooses the target."},{"name":"Political Immunity","desc":"[MON] expends a **political capital** to cast shield."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"wis","order":4},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"persuasion","stat":"cha"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Fiona","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}